{"tid":2294252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台美「經濟對話」簽備忘錄","createTime":"2020-11-21T01:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T01:39:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"657561508297d4571f65eca762dc6d2a0f2c12f2","tid":2294252,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201121/DB3KDGUZ7JCABC26YBHFV2ZU5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201121%2FDB3KDGUZ7JCABC26YBHFV2ZU5M%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM33vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=6e9e7f97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201121%2FDB3KDGUZ7JCABC26YBHFV2ZU5M%2F&h=ddf0b6c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201121/DB3KDGUZ7JCABC26YBHFV2ZU5M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台美「經濟對話」簽備忘錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x5-LHufMDETFKWvh-ir0QmLLLVg=/1296x865/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IOZD5KAHHNG2DJRCOVT3VMFT74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx5-LHufMDETFKWvh-ir0QmLLLVg%3D%2F1296x865%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIOZD5KAHHNG2DJRCOVT3VMFT74.jpg&h=658d0c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台美經濟繁榮夥伴對話登場，駐美代表蕭美琴（右）與美國台協會執行理事藍鶯（左）在美國國務次卿克拉克（左二）與經濟部次長陳正祺（右二）見證下，簽署備忘錄。<br />\n(蘋果新聞網)<br />\n<br />\n首屆「台美經濟繁榮夥伴對話」美東時間20日上午8時於華府四季飯店登場，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：趁拜登亞太貿易政策未明朗出招  習謀加入CPTPP做一哥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JuGEmJulRAptmkXvVzn1FkoCj64=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2ZHMF2WRAZDBRKDL4DIOTEH2NU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJuGEmJulRAptmkXvVzn1FkoCj64%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2ZHMF2WRAZDBRKDL4DIOTEH2NU.jpg&h=790c177a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■惠勒將在下月5日訪台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美環保署長下月初訪台<br />\n<br />\n據中央社報道，台灣方面由經濟部次長陳正祺在華府與美方召開實體會議；經濟部長王美花、行政院政務委員鄧振中及相關部會官員，則在台北透過視訊同步參與討論。台灣駐美代表處指出，為了彰顯台美雙方政府對對話的支持，克拉克與鄧振中共同見證備忘錄的簽署，也相互致函表達對簽署備忘錄的支持。鄧振中的致函是由陳正祺代為轉交。駐美代表處說，除簽署備忘錄外，雙方將持續就全球健康安全、科學與科技、供應鏈重組、投資審查、基礎建設及能源，與5G等議題進行討論。<br />\n<br />\n此外，台美關係繼續升溫，應台灣外交部邀請，美國環境保護署署長惠勒（Andrew Wheeler）將於下月初訪台三天，與台灣官方商討多面向的環保合作。惠勒是繼衞生部長阿扎爾、國務次卿克拉奇後，四個月內第三名訪台的美國內閣官員。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"2161e9a4beaa4cba50da7adfc2fcea5ed9345df8","tid":2294252,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"}]}